                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Its not really in the spirit of the game, but it is part of the game.  PlayerAuctions currently has millions of plat for sale on a regular basis as well as accounts and items.
<br />

<br />
If we are purchasing the rights to Sony's intellectual property, shouldn't we be able to do with it as we choose to a certain extent?
<br />

<br />
I agree with most of you, but there's no way Sony can enforce a ban on plat or item sales... so I said YES.
<br />

<br />
Plus, if a kid is going to make his money selling EQ plat instead of meth or extasy who am I to begrudge him this opportunity to stay legit.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
